_header: After the sayings of men that been hold

CULNn412.Transcription:
After þe sayyngus off men þat ben holdeoff þi good
                    frynd be nott þu to boldNo mestry yt ys a ffrynd to gettBut to
                    kepe hym wyll yt ys a proper feythet
CULNn412.Note:
Below a line of musical notes; followed by ‘Brother syster vnkylle
                    anenete / Thomas Robert Wylliam, John / Roger Edwarde Edmunde
                    Rachard’.
